<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />You have withdrawn all your wrath;</para>

<para style="q1">you have turned back from your hot anger.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Restore us, God of our salvation,</para>

<para style="q1">and let go of your displeasure with us.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Will you be angry with us forever?</para>

<para style="q1">Will you remain angry throughout future generations?</para>
